<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.6080177>
    dc:description "FIG. 6. — Labrum of genera under Pericapritermes-group;A, Dicuspiditermes incola (Wasmann,1893); B, Homallotermes pilosus (Mathur & Thapa,1962); C, Indocapritermes aruni Chhotani,1997;D, Krishnacapritermes maitii Chhotani,1997;E, Labiocapritermes distortus (Silvestri,1922);F, Pericapritermes dunensis (Roonwal & Sen-Sarma, 1960); G, Procapritermes keralai (Chhotani & Ferry, 1995); H, Pseudocapritermes fletcheri (Holmgren & Holmgren, 1917). Scale bars: A-C, 0.3 mm; D, E, H, 0.2 mm; F, G, 0.1 mm." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/6080177/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.6080181>
    dc:description "FIG. 7. — A, pronotum of Rinacapritermes silvius Amina & Rajmohana,n. gen.,n. sp. soldier; B, pronotum of Indocapritermes aruni Chhotani,1997 soldier C, mandible of Rinacapritermes abundans Amina & Rajmohana, n. gen., n. sp. soldier D, mandible of Indocapritermes aruni soldier. Scale bars: 0.2 mm." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/6080181/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.6080155>
    dc:description "FIG. 1. — Rinacapritermes silvius Amina & Rajmohana, n. gen., n. sp.: A, soldier body dorsal view; B, soldier head dorsal view; C, soldier head profile; D, soldier’s labrum; E, soldier’s postmentum; F, worker left and right mandible. Scale bars: A, B, 0.5 mm; C, F, 0.3 mm; D, 0.1 mm; E, 0.2 mm." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/6080155/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.6080159>
    dc:description "FIG. 2. — Rinacapritermes abundans Amina & Rajmohana,n. gen., n. sp.: A, soldier body dorsal view; B, soldier head dorsal view; C, soldier head profile; D, soldier’s labrum; E, soldier’s Postmentum; F, worker left and right mandible. Scale bars: A, 0.5 mm; B, F, 0.3 mm; C, 0.2 mm; D, E, 0.1 mm." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/6080159/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

